  "title": "Earthly Rich Portuguese Black Pudding Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and rich Portuguese stew featuring black pudding, this dish is perfect for a midnight craving, with a cultured and cheese-pull twist. It is a nut-free-friendly option for those with dietary restrictions.",
