  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional 1 minute.",
    "Add the sliced black pudding and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the peeled and cubed potatoes, peeled and sliced carrots, tomato paste, red wine, beef broth, salt, and black pepper, stirring to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 30 minutes.",
    "Stir in the shredded cheddar cheese until melted and well combined.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with additional cheese if desired."
